&lt;p&gt;A position has become available for a full time Band 5 staff Nurse on Ward 39. Ward 39 is a 25 bedded dual speciality area consisting of Cardiology and Cardio-Thoracic patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ward takes step-down in care of patients from CITU, CCU, elective admissions, emergency admissions from A &amp; E and Out Patient Clinics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience is not required involving both specialities as extensive training will provided.&lt;/p&gt;
